org.yamcs.xtce

Class CommandVerifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yamcs.xtce.CommandVerifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CommandVerifier
extends Object
implements Serializable
    XTCE: A command verifier is used to check that the command has been successfully executed. Command Verifiers may be either a Custom Algorithm or a Boolean Check or the presence of a Container for a relative change in the value of a Parameter. The CheckWindow is a time period where the verification must test true to pass.
